  `,paraId:0,tocIndex:0},{value:"@dext7r/hooks is a custom Hooks library for React, designed to provide a convenient and easy-to-use set of Hooks tailored for various scenarios. This library encompasses a range of common frontend request operations, including Axios, Puppeteer, Fetch, Request, and more, to facilitate efficient handling of network requests and browser interactions\u3002",paraId:1,tocIndex:0},{value:"@dext7r/hooks \u662F\u4E00\u4E2A\u57FA\u4E8E React \u7684\u81EA\u5B9A\u4E49 Hooks \u5E93\uFF0C\u65E8\u5728\u63D0\u4F9B\u4E00\u5957\u65B9\u4FBF\u3001\u6613\u7528\u7684\u9488\u5BF9\u4E0D\u540C\u573A\u666F\u7684 Hooks \u5C01\u88C5\u3002\u8BE5\u5E93\u6DB5\u76D6\u4E86\u591A\u79CD\u5E38\u89C1\u7684\u524D\u7AEF\u8BF7\u6C42\u64CD\u4F5C\uFF0C\u5305\u62EC Axios\u3001Puppeteer\u3001Fetch\u3001Request \u7B49\uFF0C\u4EE5\u5E2E\u52A9\u5F00\u53D1\u8005\u66F4\u9AD8\u6548\u5730\u5904\u7406\u7F51\u7EDC\u8BF7\u6C42\u548C\u6D4F\u89C8\u5668\u64CD\u4F5C",paraId:2,tocIndex:0},{value:"Homepage",paraId:3},{value:"\u{1F464} ",paraId:4,tocIndex:2},{value:"h7ml",paraId:4,tocIndex:2},{value:"Website: ",paraId:5,tocIndex:2},{value:"http://h7ml.cn?q=github",paraId:5,tocIndex:2},{value:"Github: ",paraId:5,tocIndex:2},{value:"@h7ml",paraId:5,tocIndex:2},{value:"Contributions, issues and feature requests are welcome!",paraId:6,tocIndex:3},{value:"Feel free to check ",paraId:6,tocIndex:3},{value:"issues page",paraId:6,tocIndex:3},{value:". You can also take a look at the ",paraId:6,tocIndex:3},{value:"contributing guide",paraId:6,tocIndex:3},{value:".",paraId:6,tocIndex:3},{value:"Give a \u2B50\uFE0F if this project helped you!",paraId:7,tocIndex:4},{value:"\u{1F4CA} Total: ",paraId:8,tocIndex:5},{value:"4",paraId:8,tocIndex:5},{value:`
